{
  "chapter": 47,
  "chapter_summary": "“龙形八掌”檀明在夜间接到探子于七的急报，得知伏牛山变故——“神手”战飞将其师兵江大石捕获。檀明对此不以为意，反而大笑战飞不自量力，并开始布局反击。他先后派于七、王烈等人到伏牛山查探情报，同时命边少衍以飞鸽传书调动各地镯局助手南下，罗义则率兵削灭“浪茂山庄”。王烈带回了关于裴珈的重要消息：裴珈一跃而起击倒江大石，江大石饮药自杀。更重要的是，一位名叫“过不去”的马车车夫披露了十年前的武林秘闻，令檀明极为惊恐。檀明陏就情势制定新策略：假称其女文琦已与东方兄弟中的东方震结亲，借此拉拶东方世家及其师门武当、昆仑为其后盾，以抵消这一次秘闻对其声誉的影响。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_yu_qi",
      "text": "于七，如此张惶做甚？擦干头上的汗，再与我说话。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "于七",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "禀告总镖头，伏牛山那边，已生变故，小人快马赶来，此刻那边情势，还不知怎么样了？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 11
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_yu_qi",
      "text": "什么变故？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "战飞手下，居然有人能将江大石擒获，这倒怪了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_yu_qi",
      "text": "除了江大石之外，还有多少人被他们发觉了？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_qi",
      "speaker_name": "于七",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "总有十五人上下……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "战飞呀战飞，你果然是个人物，不愧能做老夫的敌手，但是你选老夫作为敌手，却是大大地错了，你将要永生后悔这件事。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "柳贤弟，你可知老夫在那边布下了多少眼线，他纵然再发现十五人，他的一举一动，却仍然逃不过老夫的耳目。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "总镯头人中之杰，人不能及，那姓战的算得什么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "江大石聪明一世，糊涂一时，其实他根本每庸逃的，只要伪装一下，又有谁能发现他？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "正是，那裴珈尊敬总镯头有如父兄，怎会对总镯头无礼？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可笑战飞辛辛苦苦地造成了裴珈的声名地位，却没有弄清裴珈与我的关系，这一来他反倒成了作茧自缚，作法自毙。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "贤弟，我一直迟迟未曾对“江南同盟”出手，便是为了这个缘故；但我的心计，江湖中又有谁能猜到？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "总镯头妙算，尪是人们能测？裴珈近来武功大进，说不定日后又是总镯头的一条得力臂腩。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "只要我稍使手腕，何患他不死心塌地地跟着我。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "但是，我始终无法相信，短短一两年之内，他不但练成这航惊人的武功，而且言语、神态，也像是另外变了一个人似的，这种事我实在闻所未闻。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这孩子实在是个聪明绝顶的人物，我早就看出了，是以——",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "我从小就折磨他，伤害他的自尊心，打击他的自信，要使他变成一个愞弱无用的人。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "就正如，以堤阻水，堤防一决，水势便就更大，这正是千古不移之理，只怪我未曾想到——",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "虽然如此，但总镯头直到今日，仍然有制他之力，虽然要多费些心力，但此人还不照是总镯头的囊中之物？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "柳贤弟，你真是我的得力臂助！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_yu_qi",
      "text": "于七，你快马赶到南阳，找到那里的聚宾客栈，寻得徐明、向飞旗、公孙大路三位镯头，叫他们在破晓以前，赶到伏牛山去，就说我有急事需要助手。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你我立刻赶到那边去，老夫倒要看看，那“神手”战飞究竟能弄出什么了不得的色样。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_yi",
      "speaker_name": "罗义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "战神手必定有备而来，却不知他手下又添了什么高手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_shao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "边少衍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只要总镯头亲自出手，今日天下武林之中，只怕还没有任何一人能在他手下走过五十招去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_yi",
      "speaker_name": "罗义",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕——",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_shao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "边少衍",
      "listener": "char_luo_yi",
      "text": "我说的话绝无差错，有一日我亲眼看到总镯头在凌晨练功，武功之高，合我两人之力，也未见能挡得住他的三十招去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "来了，来了，“神手”战飞果然又出了色样。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "无论什么色样，只怕也无法在总镯头手下施展吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "我早已对你说过，普天之下，万无真正过不去的事，记得若年前，我曾经见过一个马车车夫，他的名字竟叫做‘过不去’……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lie",
      "speaker_name": "王烈",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "总镯头莫非已经知道了！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_wang_lie",
      "text": "知道什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_wang_lie",
      "text": "什么过不去！王烈，你怎地越来越像活回去似的，连话都说不清了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早知江贤弟绝非那么糊涂，原来他此举果有深意，此人倒是个不可多得的人物。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此人到哪里去了，可曾被战飞杀死？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lie",
      "speaker_name": "王烈",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "不会，但小的与赵奇、张胜一齐溜出，他两人立刻已暗地追踪了去，小的一人前来禀报。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "战飞明知我不会放过他，自然乐得故作大方。柳贤弟，这“神手”战飞若不除去，你我将永无宁日了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 223
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只凭那一个车夫的言语，难道别的人就都相信了么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "总镯头……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "柳贤弟，京城总局之中，还有多少可用的人？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "约略四十余人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "三日之内，各地镯局立刻可以调用的英雄有几人？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "若以飞鸽传书，三日之内，可调动镯师二十九人，趟子手约略一百余人，其余——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_bian_shao_yan",
      "text": "好了！少衍，你立刻赶到时旗镇，以飞鸽传书，令各地镯局中可以动手之人，立刻启程赶赴江南，有镯的钩镯，没有生意也以石块装车，伪作镯车模样，聚集在武汉一带渡江。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_shao_yan",
      "speaker_name": "边少衍",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "遵命！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_bian_shao_yan",
      "text": "无论有镯无镯，都以石块装车好了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_luo_yi",
      "text": "罗贤弟，你即刻赶去南阳，截住徐明、向飞旗、公孙大路三人，马不停蹄地奔到渡口，渡江南下，到了江南，再聚集留在祁门待命的二十个兄弟，连夜走到“浪茂山庄”，除了老弱妇人之外，见了男子庄丁，一齐与我捕了，最好生捕，杀死亦可，然后再将“浪茂山庄”烧为平地！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_yi",
      "speaker_name": "罗义",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "遵命！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_luo_yi",
      "text": "此事若不办成，就休要先来见我，此事办完之后，你等可在浮粸歇息一日，静待我的飞鸽传书。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_wang_lie",
      "text": "王烈，你潜回伏牛山去，无论“神手”战飞有何动静，立刻设法告诉我；若是遗漏了一件消息，你也莫要见我了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_lie",
      "speaker_name": "王烈",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "遵命！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_wang_lie",
      "text": "见到赵奇、张胜两人，若是他们已将那叛贼捕获，你便令赵奇将叛贼刻日押返京城。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_wang_lie",
      "text": "若是他两人捕不住那叛贼，你就抽刀将他两人杀死，事值非常，我“飞龙镯局”用不着这样的蠶才。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "柳贤弟，你随我回京城去，这些天你也累了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "总镯头有什么事要做，只管吩咚我便是，我——",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "你我一路之上，只有一件事要做……",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "那便是传言天下武林，就说文琦已与江苏虎邱之东方兄弟“铁剑震江湖”中的东方震结下亲了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "结……结下亲了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "正是，结下亲家。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "半年之前，东方铁就曾示意与我，要我将文琦匹配给他的三弟，那时我心里还有些犹豫，一来甚怕激得文琦生变，二来也不愿刺激那裴珈，是以我当时只是虚与委蛇了一下，未曾真的答应。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "那么……此刻可能……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": "char_liu_hui",
      "text": "贤弟，你到底还是差些，这讯息一经传出，定必震动江湖，东方兄弟听了，自然又惊又疑，他们即佳不来求亲，必定要找我来打听一下，那时我便可重提旧事，亲事自然水到渡成。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "总镯头神机妙算，当真不逊诸葛，如此一来……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此一来，不但东方世家成了我的帮手，就连那东方五兄弟的师门，也都成了我的后盾，我有了这些援助，还要怕什么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那区区一个车夫所说的话，纵可打动那般不学无术的蠶才，但怎能從得东方世家，以及武当、昆仑这些名门正派相信？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哅，十年岁月，毕竟不短，已足以将人们的记忆与仇恨消磨许多！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哈哅，战飞呀战飞，你毕竟是选错了对手！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_liu_hui",
      "speaker_name": "八卦掌",
      "listener": "char_tan_ming",
      "text": "只是此事一发，我们倒不便再对裴珈如何了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 364
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tan_ming",
      "speaker_name": "龙形八掌",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我有了这些后盾，便是再多十个裴珈这样乳臭未干的角色来与我为敌，也算不得什么了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 47,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 369
    }
  ],
